Read data file using config information

This is a wrapper for ct_read_data().

ct_read_data_config(file, config)

Arguments

file

character, single line, path to a file or a single string
config

list created using ct_read_config()

Value

tibble (data frame)

See also

ct_read_data()

Examples

  config <- ct_example("keating_1999.CFG") %>% ct_read_config()
  ct_example("keating_1999.DAT") %>% ct_read_data_config(config)
